cRUSTy is a shell written in Rust by [[https://github.com/Phate6660|Phate6660]] and [[https://github.com/TheOnAndOnlyZenomat|Zenomat]].

== Running ==
To run an interactive shell:\\
cargo run --release

To run a non-interactive shell with a command:\\
cargo run --release -- -c "echo test | sed s/test/success/g"

